result.name: Aji Amiyaki

reviews.text: Nice ambience but unfortunately it doesn't make up for the lackluster food.
Not bad for a Japanese set dinner, price reasonable, waiters are polite

Food is good (4 stars) but service have big room for improvement.

Arrived around 5pm (lunch sets till 5:30). Still have lunch sets but waitress don't inform us how to order the lunch set. At a result, we paid for the original price for the sets (without complimentary juice). Moreover, staff are having their dinner on the same time and nearly no service at all. Very disappointed about the service. Downgrade 2 stars on this visit. :(

We ordered three sets. Eel are very good: juicy and thick. Spain Kurobuta Udon (西班牙黑豚腩肉烏冬) is excellent. Meat are tenderly made and rice in pork flavour. The seasoned egg is great and yolk are semi-cooked (流心). Soup and udon are excellent. But the rice is too humid this time (too much water added when preparing).

11 Feb 2018

=============
Not a big restaurant. But quite many foods to choose from. Famous for Japanese beef.
Ordered two sets. All sets with miso soap, seasoned seaweed (中華沙律) and salad. Salad is fresh and soap is good. Eel set is just $88 but is out of my expectations. Eel is thick and juicy. Another set is Deluxe Japan Wagyu (飛驒牛 - 日本黑毛和牛). The beef is tender, juicy, dissolved in the mouth and rich in beef flavor. It's terrific. Highly recommended for this restaurant (esp for the beef).

May join the Yummy Club free for 2 years (accumulated $500 within 31 days) in order to have 5% discount for their chained restaurants.

Liquor licence under application. 2017-12-25
Seating and environment are comfort, but the beef is bit pricy compared to the quality, have room to improve
Fair food long queue

reviews.text: A nice shopping mall with nice aesthetics and designs. Though the brands weren't that popular, the restaurants made the shopping mall better.

A shopping mall that having variety of restaurants. The top floor is a cinema, while the second floor is a podium. The mall function as a supplement to Marittime square, where you can spend whole day for shopping.
Cozy shopping arcade with food venues. New!
Car Park maybe too difficult for new driver. Becareful when exiting the carpark, very narrow exit.
Very nice selection of shops. Awesome outdoor spaces and views. One of the better MTR malls.

reviews.text: 都算ok不似新鴻嘅商場只有高檔嘅嘢🤔消費平貴任君選擇👍新鴻基嘅商場😤強姦錢包！全部係連鎖名店🤕

青衣城二期開咗都無正式的入去行過，每次都是去青衣站搭地鐵時經過，同家人去睇戲就順便行吓及食個午餐。
青衣城二期於一樓設有行人天橋連接著一期及青衣地鐵站，同時亦連接著巴士總站，交通便利，盡佔地理優勢。
商場環境當然同一期無得比啦(一期大好多)，話雖有幾層，但每層都是一個框框一陣就行完，行人通道感覺不太寬闊有少許窄，唯一覺得不錯的是食肆比較集中，價格方面也不是全部走高檔路線，屬中上的類別，底層更有大路的連鎖食肆，相對較為大眾化，加上戲院設於商場三樓，將食客分流到這邊，打造成行街睇戲食飯連貫一起，又可以不用在一期那邊咁擠擁揾食；另外頂層是天台花園及2樓有露天公園，如行得累的話上去坐吓都不錯的 。
' 包羅萬有同埋佢鄰近西鐵站交通方便
地下米線陣，大家樂，一粥麵長期咁多人

reviews.text: A good shopping mall and it is massive.  They do displays for special occasions which is really cute.  It is situated next to the MTR station which is convenient.

Nice slightly out of the noise and smoke along the tourist belt..Great food and feeling.
Just nice to walk through the tourist area and then walk into pleasant outdoor drinking and eating.  Local favorites area.
good location with convenient MTR service, other public transportation facilities
If you are on the way to HK airport with some spare time and keen to save money, stop over here and buy, eat and relax at half airport prices
Shopping mall with loads of chain and smaller boutique like stores. Food choices are varied. Really good dim sum downstairs in the well.
